      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Chris McConnell</b>\n</p><p><b>Christopher C. McConnell</b>,<br />\nan American computer scientist and <a href=\"/Microsoft\" title=\"Microsoft\">Microsoft</a> employee, alumnus from the <a href=\"/Carnegie_Mellon_University\" title=\"Carnegie Mellon University\">Carnegie Mellon University</a>. \nAt CMU as P.D. Student, Chris McConnell worked with <a href=\"/Hans_Berliner\" title=\"Hans Berliner\">Berliner</a> on the chess program <a href=\"/HiTech\" title=\"HiTech\">HiTech</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>, and was involved in researching the <a href=\"/B*\" title=\"B*\">B*</a> probability based <a href=\"/Search\" title=\"Search\">search</a> and in <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">tuning</a> <a href=\"/Evaluation\" title=\"Evaluation\">evaluation</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#What_links_here.3F\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">What links here?</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chris_McConnell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Chris McConnell</a> (<b>1995</b>). <i>Minimal Model Complexity Search</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/epia/epia95.html\">EPIA 1995</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Hans_Berliner\" title=\"Hans Berliner\">Hans Berliner</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Chris McConnell</a> (<b>1995</b>). <i>B* Probability Based Search.</i> <a href=\"/Carnegie_Mellon_University\" title=\"Carnegie Mellon University\">Carnegie Mellon University</a>, research report, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://pdfs.semanticscholar.org/95c8/569d34c3b7bc94f98b159825bd66a8b5e75d.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Chris McConnell</a> (<b>1995</b>). <i>Tuning Evaluation Functions for Search</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://citeseerx.ist.psu.edu/viewdoc/download;jsessionid=9B2A0CCA8B1AFB594A879799D974111A?doi=10.1.1.53.9742&amp;rep=rep1&amp;type=pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Chris McConnell</a> (<b>1995</b>). <i>Tuning Evaluation Functions for Search</i> (Talk), <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.cmu.edu/afs/cs.cmu.edu/user/ccm/www/talks/tune.ps\">ps</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Hans_Berliner\" title=\"Hans Berliner\">Hans Berliner</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Chris McConnell</a> (<b>1996</b>). <i>B* probability based search</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Artificial_Intelligence_%28journal%29\">Artificial Intelligence</a>, Vol. 86, No. 1</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chris_McConnell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.cmu.edu/afs/cs.cmu.edu/user/ccm/www/home.html\">Chris McConnell's PhD Student homepage</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/person.php?id=195\">Chris McConnell's ICGA Tournaments</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://blogs.msdn.microsoft.com/e7/2008/10/13/windows-desktop-search/\">Engineering Windows 7 - Windows Desktop Search</a> by Chris McConnell, October 13, 2008</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chris_McConnell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/person.php?id=195\">Chris McConnell's ICGA Tournaments</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/m/McConnell:Chris.html\">dblp: Chris McConnell</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"What_links_here.3F\">What links here?</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chris_McConnell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: What links here?\">edit</a><span 